#: ../../docs/classes/class_particles2d.rst:19
msgid ""
"2D particle node used to create a variety of particle systems and "
"effects. ``Particles2D`` features an emitter that generates some number "
"of particles at a given rate."
msgstr "用于创建各种粒子系统和效果的2D粒子节点。``Particles2D`` 具有一个发射器，该发射器以给定的速率，生成一定数量的粒子。"

#: ../../docs/classes/class_particles2d.rst:21
msgid ""
"Use the ``process_material`` property to add a :ref:`ParticlesMaterial "
"<class_ParticlesMaterial>` to configure particle appearance and behavior."
" Alternatively, you can add a :ref:`ShaderMaterial "
"<class_ShaderMaterial>` which will be applied to all particles."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``process_material`` 属性添加一个 :ref:`ParticlesMaterial "
"<class_ParticlesMaterial>` 来配置粒子外观和行为。另外，您可以添加一个 :ref:`ShaderMaterial "
"<class_ShaderMaterial>`，它将应用于所有粒子。"

